OL,3,C#2.5m works to replace RAAC starts
OL,4,Cnext month
OL,6,FRAAC roof replacement works of the
OL,7,FSands Centre auditorium will start
OL,8,Fnext month, costing up to #2.5m.
OL,10,FParts of The Sands Centre Auditorium,
OL,11,Fin Carlisle, were temporarily closed
OL,12,Flast year after an assessment found
OL,13,FReinforced Autoclaved Aerated
OL,14,FConcrete, known as RAAC, in the
OL,15,Fauditorium of the events centre.
OL,17,FThe #2.5m has been secured within
OL,18,Fexisting council capital budgets and
OL,19,Fthe works are expected to be completed
OL,20,Fby spring 2025.
