OL,3,C#2.5m works to replace RAAC starts
OL,4,Cnext month
OL,6,FA recommendation to replace the RAAC
OL,7,Fpanels in the auditorium roof was put
OL,8,Fforward after specialist engineers
OL,9,Fcarried out a detailed structural
OL,10,Fassessment last year.
OL,12,FThe assessment occurred following the
OL,13,Fchange in guidance from the previous
OL,14,Fgovernment's guidance on the use of
OL,15,FRAAC in buildings.
