OL,3,C#2.5m works to replace RAAC starts
OL,4,Cnext month
OL,6,FThe construction phase will begin in
OL,7,FSeptember after Cumberland Council
OL,8,Fappointed Cubby Construction Ltd, a
OL,9,FCarlisle-based contractor, following
OL,10,Fthe agreement of a design for the
OL,11,Freplacement of RAAC panels.
OL,13,FInternal improvements to the
OL,14,Fauditorium will also take place,
OL,15,Fincluding imporvements to seating and
OL,16,Fupgrades to the back-of-house
OL,17,Ffacilities.
