OL,3,C#2.5m works to replace RAAC starts
OL,4,Cnext month
OL,6,FCllr Mark Fryer, Leader of Cumberland
OL,7,FCouncil, says it is "fantastic that
OL,8,Fthis project is entering its next
OL,9,Fphase".
OL,11,FHe said: "This is an essential
OL,12,Finvestment in one of the region's
OL,13,Fpremier entertainment venues and once
OL,14,Fcompleted will see the return of an
OL,15,Fimproved venue for our residents,
OL,16,Fbusinesses and visitors."
