OL,3,C#2.5m works to replace RAAC starts
OL,4,Cnext month
OL,6,FGLL, who manages the venue on the
OL,7,Fcouncil's behalf, moved their
OL,8,Fclassical concert programme to the
OL,9,Fsports hall within The Sands after the
OL,10,Fclosure of the auditorium last year.
OL,12,FThe day-to-day running of the main
OL,13,Fleisure centre will not be impacted by
OL,14,Fthe works.
OL,16,FThe new main Sands Centre building's
OL,17,Fleisure provision is unaffected, which
OL,18,Fincludes the pools, gym, studios and
OL,19,Fsports hall.
