OL,3,C#2.5m works to replace RAAC starts
OL,4,Cnext month
OL,6,FA Spokesperson for GLL said: "We are
OL,7,Fexcited that the works are now
OL,8,Fprogressing to the construction phase
OL,9,Fand can't wait to welcome audiences
OL,10,Fback to the venue in Spring 2025.
OL,12,F"We look forward to working with
OL,13,FCumberland Council and Cubby
OL,14,FConstruction Ltd to establish a
OL,15,Freopening date and hosting top-class
OL,16,Fentertainment in Carlisle once again.
